        LEFT JOIN 
        (
            SELECT m1.MenuItemsItemID, m1.RestaurantsRestaurantID, r0.RestaurantID, r0.ClosingHours, r0.OpeningHours, r0.RestaurantAddress, r0.RestaurantDescription, r0.RestaurantEmail, r0.RestaurantName, r0.RestaurantPhone

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [m1].[MenuItemsItemID], [m1].[RestaurantsRestaurantID], [r0].[RestaurantID], [r0].[ClosingHours], [r0].[OpeningHours], [r0].[RestaurantAddress], [r0].[RestaurantDescription], [r0].[RestaurantEmail], [r0].[RestaurantName], [r0].[RestaurantPhone]

) AS [t] ON [m].[ItemID] = [t].[MenuItemsItemID]

    SELECT [m1].[MenuItemsItemID], [m1].[RestaurantsRestaurantID], [r0].[RestaurantID], [r0].[ClosingHours], [r0].[OpeningHours], [r0].[RestaurantAddress], [r0].[RestaurantDescription], [r0].[RestaurantEmail], [r0].[RestaurantName], [r0].[RestaurantPhone]

) AS [t] ON [m].[ItemID] = [t].[MenuItemsItemID]

    SELECT [m1].[MenuItemsItemID], [m1].[RestaurantsRestaurantID], [r0].[RestaurantID], [r0].[ClosingHours], [r0].[OpeningHours], [r0].[RestaurantAddress], [r0].[RestaurantDescription], [r0].[RestaurantEmail], [r0].[RestaurantName], [r0].[RestaurantPhone]

) AS [t] ON [m].[ItemID] = [t].[MenuItemsItemID]

    FROM [MenuItemsRestaurant] AS [m0]

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [m1].[MenuItemsItemID], [m1].[RestaurantsRestaurantID], [r0].[RestaurantID], [r0].[ClosingHours], [r0].[OpeningHours], [r0].[RestaurantAddress], [r0].[RestaurantDescription], [r0].[RestaurantEmail], [r0].[RestaurantName], [r0].[RestaurantPhone]

    INNER JOIN [Restaurants] AS [r0] ON [m1].[RestaurantsRestaurantID] = [r0].[RestaurantID]
) AS [t] ON [m].[ItemID] = [t].[MenuItemsItemID]

    FROM [MenuItemsRestaurant] AS [m0]

    SELECT [m1].[MenuItemsItemID], [m1].[RestaurantsRestaurantID], [r0].[RestaurantID], [r0].[ClosingHours], [r0].[OpeningHours], [r0].[RestaurantAddress], [r0].[RestaurantDescription], [r0].[RestaurantEmail], [r0].[RestaurantName], [r0].[RestaurantPhone]

) AS [t] ON [m].[ItemID] = [t].[MenuItemsItemID]

) AS [t]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[ItemID] = [t0].[MenuItemsItemID]

FROM [Menus] AS [m]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [m1].[MenuItemsItemID], [m1].[RestaurantsRestaurantID], [r0].[RestaurantID], [r0].[ClosingHours], [r0].[OpeningHours], [r0].[RestaurantAddress], [r0].[RestaurantDescription], [r0].[RestaurantEmail], [r0].[RestaurantName], [r0].[RestaurantPhone]

) AS [t] ON [m].[ItemID] = [t].[MenuItemsItemID]

) AS [t]

    SELECT [m].[MenuItemsItemID], [m].[RestaurantsRestaurantID], [m0].[ItemID], [m0].[AvailabilityStatus], [m0].[CategoryID], [m0].[CuisineType], [m0].[DietaryInfo], [m0].[ImageURL], [m0].[Ingredients], [m0].[ItemDescription], [m0].[ItemName], [m0].[ItemPrice], [m0].[Rating], [m0].[TasteInfo]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[RestaurantID] = [t0].[RestaurantsRestaurantID]

) AS [t]

    SELECT [m].[MenuItemsItemID], [m].[RestaurantsRestaurantID], [m0].[ItemID], [m0].[AvailabilityStatus], [m0].[CategoryID], [m0].[CuisineType], [m0].[DietaryInfo], [m0].[ImageURL], [m0].[Ingredients], [m0].[ItemDescription], [m0].[ItemName], [m0].[ItemPrice], [m0].[Rating], [m0].[TasteInfo]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[RestaurantID] = [t0].[RestaurantsRestaurantID]

2024-10-08 00:43:08.043 +05:30 [DBG] Executing DbCommand [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[ItemName], [t].[Rating], [t].[ItemID], [t0].[RestaurantName], [t0].[RestaurantAddress], [t0].[MenuItemsItemID], [t0].[RestaurantsRestaurantID], [t0].[RestaurantID]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [m].[ItemName], [m].[Rating], [m].[ItemID]
    FROM [Menus] AS [m]
    ORDER BY [m].[Rating] DESC
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [r].[RestaurantName], [r].[RestaurantAddress], [m0].[MenuItemsItemID], [m0].[RestaurantsRestaurantID], [r].[RestaurantID]
